## 🛠️ Agile Ceremonies: The QA Contribution

| Ceremony | QA's Strategic Input |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Sprint Planning** | Identifying risks regarding testing environments and data requirements. |
| **Daily Stand-up** | Highlighting "Blockers" immediately to maintain sprint velocity. |
| **Sprint Review** | Presenting quality metrics, accessibility wins, and demoing features to stakeholders. |
| **Retrospective** | Proposing process improvements to mitigate recurring quality issues. |

---

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Core Philosophy:** Aim to be a **Quality Advocate**, not "Quality Police." Collaboration and shared responsibility are the keys to Agile success.
